00:08:50,881 --> 00:08:52,674
我的意思是，你所能利用的只有他的笔记
I mean, all you have to go on are his notes.

164
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:55,844
他和他的伙伴一直工作到最后一刻
He and his team worked until the last possible moment.

165
00:08:55,927 --> 00:08:57,804
他们知道 Wraith的舰队就在头顶上
They knew the Wraith ships were overhead

166
00:08:57,804 --> 00:09:00,015
但仍然在晚上头头的工作,
and still they worked through the night,

167
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:02,351
希望能找到更有力的发现,
hoping to provide one more insight,

168
00:09:02,392 --> 00:09:05,437
不是为了他们自己
one last thread of knowledge not for themselves

169
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:08,941
而是为了下一代
but for the generation that would survive.

170
00:09:13,403 --> 00:09:17,574
为了能为他们创造这一点点宝贵的时间，成千上万的士兵们牺牲了性命
Ten thousand soldiers gave their lives
to give them those last few hours.

171
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:22,204
Ferrel's 日记上的最后一句话，所有Hoffans人都知道
The last words of Ferrel's journal
are known to all Hoffans.

172
00:09:23,872 --> 00:09:26,333
我不是冒犯, Perna
I meant no disrespect, Perna.

173
00:09:28,001 --> 00:09:29,211
没关系
It's alright.

174
00:09:30,671 --> 00:09:33,173
在那时候，不止是他的日记留下了
More than just his journals survived the culling.

175
00:09:33,507 --> 00:09:36,885
他的研究材料也被保存得很好,
His research materials were safeguarded as well,

176
00:09:38,470 --> 00:09:43,475
包括细心保存的幽灵细胞的样本
including carefully preserved Wraith cell samples

177
00:09:43,475 --> 00:09:46,186
我们现在仍然可以利用
which we still use in our work today.

178
00:09:46,979 --> 00:09:47,688
请
Please.

179
00:09:52,401 --> 00:09:53,610
你自己看
See for yourself.

180
00:10:03,704 --> 00:10:04,579
哦!
Oh!

181
00:10:07,082 --> 00:10:08,375
简直是难以置信!
That's incredible!

182
00:10:16,341 --> 00:10:18,260
我亲眼看到了, Weir博士
I saw it with my own eyes, Doctor Weir.

183
00:10:18,343 --> 00:10:19,303
是的，在这个培养皿里,
Yes, in a Petri dish,

184
00:10:19,303 --> 00:10:22,556
我们谈论的是150多年前的幽灵的细胞
and we are talking about
a hundred and fifty year old Wraith cells.

185
00:10:22,764 --> 00:10:24,766
我的意思是，他们现在对这些药物已经免疫了,
I mean, for all we know, they could be immune to
the drug by now,

186
00:10:24,766 --> 00:10:26,184
或者找别的东西对付它
or come up with defences against it.

187
00:10:26,268 --> 00:10:27,603
嗯，我不这么想，博士
Well, I don't think so, Doctor.

188
00:10:27,728 --> 00:10:29,855
我使用了一点研究人员的特权
I took the liberty of running a few tests of my own

189
00:10:29,896 --> 00:10:30,647
使用了一些
using cells taken

190
00:10:30,772 --> 00:10:33,900
Sheppard少校从Athos带回的幽灵的胳膊上个的细胞
from the Wraith arm
Major Sheppard brought back from Athos.

191
00:10:34,151 --> 00:10:34,985
结果还是一样
The results were the same...

192
00:10:34,985 --> 00:10:37,321
几乎可以完全抵抗
near complete resistance.

193
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,489
这其中肯定有点什么
They've definitely got something.

194
00:10:39,531 --> 00:10:41,116
相信我，我比任何人都觉得惊讶
Believe me, I'm more surprised than anyone.

195
00:10:41,158 --> 00:10:42,284
所以你的建议是?
So what do you recommend?

196
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:46,038
我们将他们的工作推向另一个水准
That we take their work to the next level.

197
00:10:46,121 --> 00:10:49,207
我已经通知了 Hoffans ，我们有客人
I've informed the Hoffans of our guest in the brig.

198
00:10:49,958 --> 00:10:52,002
你知道你在说什么么?
You realise what you're asking for?

199
00:10:52,377 --> 00:10:53,754
我知道
I do.

200
00:11:02,012 --> 00:11:03,889
有什么新情况,军士?
Anything I should know about, Sergeant?

201
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:05,474
没有，长官，他很安静
No, sir, he's been quiet.

202
00:11:06,058 --> 00:11:07,684
还在试图让你看到什么?
Still trying to make you see things?

203
00:11:07,726 --> 00:11:09,144
他已经放弃了
He's given up on that.

204
00:11:10,187 --> 00:11:12,064
我觉得他坚持不了多久
I didn't think he'd last this long.

205
00:11:23,158 --> 00:11:25,619
又见面了, Sheppard少校
Hello again, Major Sheppard.

206
00:11:29,998 --> 00:11:32,209
很抱歉，如果我打搅了你
Sorry if I woke you.

207
00:11:32,501 --> 00:11:35,045
只是过来看看你有什么需要
Just came by to see if there's anything you needed.

208
00:11:35,587 --> 00:11:37,464
杂志，干净的毛巾
Magazine, fresh towels.

209
00:11:38,298 --> 00:11:41,510
你没有很好的掩饰你的恐惧, 少校
You hide your fear poorly, Major.

210
00:11:42,052 --> 00:11:44,888
你知道的，我们像这样谈话已经好几个星期了,
Y'know, we've been having these conversations
for a couple of weeks now,

211
00:11:44,888 --> 00:11:47,265
但我还不知道你的名字
and I don't even know your name.

212
00:11:47,891 --> 00:11:49,226
你们也有名字，对吧?
You guys do have names, right?

213
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:51,228
让我猜猜
Let me guess...

214
00:11:52,688 --> 00:11:53,689
Steve?
Steve?

215
00:11:53,939 --> 00:11:55,190
我是你的死神
I am your death.

216
00:11:55,774 --> 00:11:58,235
你只要知道这个就够了
That is all you need to know.

217
00:11:58,735 --> 00:12:00,654
我更喜欢Steve
I prefer Steve.

218
00:12:06,243 --> 00:12:08,078
你想要什么?
What do you hope to gain from this?

219
00:12:08,287 --> 00:12:12,916
我只是想更加了解你们一些，打破我们之间的隔阂
Just trying to bridge the gap between
our two cultures; get to know you better.

220
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,627
试试看如何让你变温和一些
That and try to figure out how to keep your kind

221
00:12:15,627 --> 00:12:18,755
从上百万无辜的人那里获得生命
from sucking the life
out of millions of innocent people.

222
00:12:18,797 --> 00:12:21,383
就算我告诉你那些你想知道的东西,
Even if I told you what you want to know,

223
00:12:21,675 --> 00:12:24,386
也不会改变什么
it would change nothing.

224
00:12:24,469 --> 00:12:29,725
你的命运和那些阻碍我们的人类一样
You are doomed as are any humans that stand in our way.

225
00:12:29,850 --> 00:12:32,060
没有更好的死法了么?
Can't be a nice way to die?

226
00:12:32,644 --> 00:12:33,437
饥饿,
Hungry,

227
00:12:33,937 --> 00:12:34,938
慢慢的,
slow,

228
00:12:36,148 --> 00:12:39,776
你的食物
knowing your food source is just...

229
00:12:39,985 --> 00:12:41,903
看得见摸不着
out of reach.

230
00:12:43,155 --> 00:12:44,573
为什么把我关在这里?
Why do you keep me here?

231
00:12:44,656 --> 00:12:46,783
我要知道我们将要面临的是什么
I need to know what we're up against.

232
00:12:46,908 --> 00:12:47,826
比如说,
For example,

233
00:12:48,493 --> 00:12:51,747
你们到底有多少这种大的飞船，它们在哪里?
how many of those big hive ships
have you got and where are they?

234
00:12:51,872 --> 00:12:54,291
告诉你有什么好处
You have nothing to offer me in return.

235
00:12:56,668 --> 00:13:00,797
或许我们会给你吃的
We could talk about easing your hunger...

236
00:13:01,423 --> 00:13:03,342
Steve
Steve.

237
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,845
你不会牺牲你的同类的
You would never sacrifice one of your own kind.

238
00:13:08,013 --> 00:13:11,099
它们就站在
And yet, it is all that stands between

239
00:13:11,141 --> 00:13:14,561
你和你找寻的那些信息之间
you and the information you seek.

240
00:13:25,864 --> 00:13:29,451
现在我们唯一的资源就是活的幽灵细胞
Using living Wraith cells
is our only recourse at this juncture.

241
00:13:29,701 --> 00:13:33,455
否则我们无法确信这种药物是否有用
Without them we have no way of knowing
for certain if the drug is actually viable.

242
00:13:33,538 --> 00:13:35,707
你说过它
You said it worked effectively on the cells

243
00:13:35,707 --> 00:13:37,584
对我们带回来的那只幽灵胳膊上的细胞是很有效的
of the severed Wraith arm we brought back.

244
00:13:37,668 --> 00:13:38,043
的确如此
It did.

245
00:13:38,752 --> 00:13:41,964
但是它有很多地方已经腐烂了
But those were already in a partially decayed state.

246
00:13:42,422 --> 00:13:44,299
我们需要活的样品
We need live samples.

247
00:13:44,424 --> 00:13:45,801
如果有新的样品
And with new samples

248
00:13:45,801 --> 00:13:48,095
你就可以研制出药物原型?
you think it's possible to create a prototype?

249
00:13:48,637 --> 00:13:50,389
只要有足够的时间，我就可以
Given enough time, yes I do.

250
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:52,683
他已经突破了困扰 Hoffans的地方了
He's got a good point
the Hoffans are practically obsessed.

251
00:13:52,724 --> 00:13:53,684
谢谢, Rodney
Thank you, Rodney.

252
00:13:53,725 --> 00:13:54,476
我同意, 博士
I agree, Doctor.

253
00:13:54,810 --> 00:13:57,562
但是那对于他们来说或许没什么
But their obsession may become their undoing.

254
00:13:57,771 --> 00:14:00,983
嗯，不管怎样，对我们总有好处
Well, even if they do... undo, it'd be good for us.

255
00:14:01,108 --> 00:14:03,151
我的意思是，如果有机会，难道你不想注射这样的疫苗么?
I mean, given the choice, wouldn't you want to be immune?

256
00:14:03,318 --> 00:14:06,280
否则就要成为幽灵的食物
Not if it meant the lives
the Wraith might otherwise spare.

257
00:14:07,155 --> 00:14:11,326
除非每一个人，每一个角落都有这样的免疫力,
This drug would only be of value if everyone,

258
00:14:11,326 --> 00:14:13,829
这药才是真正有用的
everywhere, possessed the same immunity.

259
00:14:14,162 --> 00:14:16,665
这个想法倒是不错
There's a thought worth pursuing.

260
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:17,582
我同意
I agree.

261
00:14:18,542 --> 00:14:21,670
少校,跟你的犯人有什么新的进展了么?
Major, have you made any progress with your prisoner?

262
00:14:21,795 --> 00:14:24,131
没有，他眨了下眼睛
Well, not yet, but he just blinked.

263
00:14:24,798 --> 00:14:25,590
眨眼?
He blinked?

264
00:14:25,716 --> 00:14:27,009
这是什么意思?
What does that mean?

265
00:14:27,467 --> 00:14:29,261
说明他仍然有把握
It means he's still holding on

266
00:14:29,261 --> 00:14:31,805
他好像暗示说他很快就可以出去了
but he's indicated to me that he may break soon.

267
00:14:31,930 --> 00:14:33,223
他告诉你这个，然后
And he indicated this to you by...

268
00:14:33,223 --> 00:14:34,474
眨眼?
blinking?

269
00:14:34,641 --> 00:14:35,642
是的
Yes.

270
00:14:36,435 --> 00:14:39,521
没有攻击, 少校,
但是到目前为止，他什么也没告诉你
No offence, Major,
but so far he hasn't told you a thing.

271
00:14:39,563 --> 00:14:40,981
他只是在拖延
For all we know he could linger

272
00:14:41,023 --> 00:14:42,816
拖几个月，然后
this way for months and ultimately

273
00:14:43,066 --> 00:14:44,943
我们仍然什么都不知道
we'll learn nothing.

274
00:14:44,985 --> 00:14:47,654
当我们说话的时候，幽灵们可能已经向着Hoff来了
The Wraith could be on their way to Hoff as we speak.

275
00:14:47,696 --> 00:14:51,408
如果你的犯人对于新药的研制有关键作用,
If your prisoner holds the key
to the creation of this drug,

276
00:14:52,326 --> 00:14:54,494
should we not take advantage of this?
should we not take advantage of this?

277
00:14:54,536 --> 00:14:57,289
我们怎样才能安全的从他身上取得样本呢?
How can we get the sample off him safely?

278
00:14:57,331 --> 00:14:59,833
我们仍然有当时抓住他的武器
We still possess the weapons used in his capture.

279
00:14:59,875 --> 00:15:03,128
让他再次束手就擒是件容易的事情
It would be a simple matter of incapacitating him again.

280
00:15:03,462 --> 00:15:04,379
所以，这是可能的?
So, then, it's possible?

281
00:15:04,671 --> 00:15:06,214
当然可能
It's possible.

282
00:15:15,349 --> 00:15:16,642
嗨, Steve
Hi, Steve.

283
00:15:18,101 --> 00:15:19,519
再见, Steve
Bye, Steve.

284
00:15:32,282 --> 00:15:33,617
博士
Doctor.

285
00:15:34,785 --> 00:15:35,911
他
Is he...

286
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:38,080
我是说，你确定他
I mean, you're certain he's...

287
00:15:38,163 --> 00:15:38,997
他已经昏过去了, 博士
He's down, Doc.

288
00:15:39,498 --> 00:15:40,666
做你想做的事情吧
Do your thing.

289
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:49,675
看起来很无害，不是么?
Almost looks peaceful, doesn't he?

290
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,425
无害?!
Peaceful?!

291
00:15:50,801 --> 00:15:52,928
你简直是昏头了!
You're out of your bloody mind!

292
00:16:05,524 --> 00:16:08,193
我重来没见过这样的设备!
I have never seen devices such as these!

293
00:16:08,652 --> 00:16:09,903
你的工作正在做最后的提炼
The work you've done refining

294
00:16:09,903 --> 00:16:11,738
这种药物应该很快就好了
the drug has been good up til now.

295
00:16:11,863 --> 00:16:15,284
有了这个我们能做得更好
With all this we can make it better.

296
00:16:17,119 --> 00:16:18,078
我觉得,
From what I can tell,

297
00:16:18,078 --> 00:16:20,831
你现在最关键的是接种的测试
your biggest problem is that the test inoculations

298
00:16:20,956 --> 00:16:22,207
现在还不能证实
failed to show enough of a presence

299
00:16:22,207 --> 00:16:24,418
这对人体是有效的
in human cells to be effective.

300
00:16:24,501 --> 00:16:26,295
我们需要的是一个更好的传输系统
What we need is a better delivery system.

301
00:16:26,336 --> 00:16:27,045
正是
Exactly.

302
00:16:27,045 --> 00:16:29,923
现在最好是先别管那些关键的蛋白质
And the best place to start
is to recreate the key protein

303
00:16:30,007 --> 00:16:32,175
来看看血清吧
in the serum and work our way up from there.

304
00:16:32,259 --> 00:16:32,926
如果我们可以避免
If we can avoid having

305
00:16:32,926 --> 00:16:34,761
它的自我重造,
to re-engineer it from a natural source,

306
00:16:34,845 --> 00:16:37,556
制成一个完全人工的版本,
and make an entirely synthetic version,

307
00:16:37,556 --> 00:16:40,100
这样它的有效性将大大提升
it should ultimately increase the efficiency.

308
00:16:40,267 --> 00:16:41,602
这可能么?
Such a thing is possible?

309
00:16:41,727 --> 00:16:44,938
只要你愿意努力试试，没什么不可能
Anything's possible if you're willing to give it a go.

310
00:16:46,106 --> 00:16:48,817
那还说什么，赶紧开始吧
C'mon then, a bald head is soon shaved.

311
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:52,529
你和其他人的口音有点不同
You speak differently than the others.

312
00:16:53,905 --> 00:16:55,907
发现了么?!
Noticed that, did you?!

313
00:16:56,325 --> 00:16:57,659
很抱歉如果我把你弄迷糊了
Sorry if I confuse you.

314
00:16:57,659 --> 00:17:01,622
相信我，我的家乡,
这起了很大的作用
Trust me, where I come from,
it all makes perfect sense.

315
00:17:01,747 --> 00:17:02,873
那里什么样子?
What is it like?

316
00:17:02,998 --> 00:17:05,417
苏格兰？哦，那里很美
Scotland? Oh, I think it's beautiful.

317
00:17:06,001 --> 00:17:08,420
但我听说这是一种嗜好
But I'm told it's something of an acquired taste.

318
00:17:08,545 --> 00:17:09,463
我是说你的世界
I meant your world.

319
00:17:10,172 --> 00:17:11,882
那儿一定很和平,
It must be so peaceful there,

320
00:17:11,923 --> 00:17:13,508
因为幽灵不会去
knowing that the Wraith will not come.

321
00:17:13,634 --> 00:17:16,303
哦，你一定很惊讶，那里一点也不和平
Oh, you'd be surprised how not peaceful it is.

322
00:17:18,388 --> 00:17:21,224
人们都很堕落
We're spoiled rotten, now that I think of it.

323
00:17:22,559 --> 00:17:23,185
你错过了
You miss it.

324
00:17:23,226 --> 00:17:25,103
对不起，让你难过了
I'm sorry for enquiring.

325
00:17:25,187 --> 00:17:27,230
哦，没关系，没关系，亲爱的
Oh, no, no. Don't be, love.

326
00:19:00,991 --> 00:19:02,034
Perna!
Perna!

327
00:19:18,425 --> 00:19:20,135
所有细胞都渗透了．
One hundred percent cellular penetration

328
00:19:20,177 --> 00:19:21,887
在所有的5次接种测试里
in all five test inoculations.

329
00:19:21,928 --> 00:19:22,763
简直是难以置信啊!
Incredible!

330
00:19:22,888 --> 00:19:24,514
仍然还有很多数据需要分析
There's still a lot of data to be analysed

331
00:19:24,514 --> 00:19:27,225
不过我相信，这个最初的结果是很棒的
but the initial results are very promising, I agree.

332
00:19:27,351 --> 00:19:31,063
Beckett 的努力让这个项目加快发展
Doctor Beckett's efforts
have advanced the project by decades.

333
00:19:31,271 --> 00:19:33,273
Perna的那些公式正在运作着
Perna's formula was right on track.

334
00:19:33,398 --> 00:19:35,901
这是改变了它的分子构成
It was just a matter of changing its molecular design

335
00:19:35,901 --> 00:19:38,153
这样的话，更加便于身体的吸收
so it could be better absorbed by the body.

336
00:19:38,528 --> 00:19:41,073
博士，这对于人民们来说是个巨大的胜利
This is an enormous victory for our people, Doctor.

337
00:19:41,156 --> 00:19:42,532
我不知道该如何感谢你
I don't know how to thank you.

338
00:19:42,658 --> 00:19:43,325
不需要
No need.

339
00:19:43,367 --> 00:19:45,994
当然，这只是初步阶段
Of course, it's only a preliminary.

340
00:19:46,536 --> 00:19:49,206
你什么时候可以开始下一步测试?
How soon until you can set up the next stage of testing?

341
00:19:49,331 --> 00:19:51,833
今天晚点时候我会把进程给您，长官
You'll have a schedule later today, Chancellor.

342
00:19:53,085 --> 00:19:55,045
抱歉，下一步?
I'm sorry next stage?

343
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:56,672
你的报告已经说得很清楚了
Your report makes it abundantly clear that

344
00:19:56,672 --> 00:19:59,716
这个项目正准备进行下一个阶段
the project is ready to proceed to its next phase.

345
00:19:59,883 --> 00:20:03,220
我们想用你的犯人测试一下血清的有效性
We want to test the serum's
effectiveness against your prisoner.

346
00:20:11,403 --> 00:20:13,072
你赞成?
And you support this?

347
00:20:13,197 --> 00:20:14,865
嗯，我知道他肯定是要死的
Well, I know for certain he's gonna die

348
00:20:14,907 --> 00:20:16,408
所以或许我们应该好好利用他
so we might as well make good use of him

349
00:20:16,450 --> 00:20:17,951
当他还活着的时候
while he's still alive.

350
00:20:18,077 --> 00:20:20,204
你真的了解日内瓦协定
You do understand the Geneva Convention

351
00:20:20,204 --> 00:20:24,041
禁止用犯人做科学试验?
prohibits using prisoners for scientific experiments?

352
00:20:24,083 --> 00:20:25,834
没有关系，博士，幽灵又没有
No offence, Doc, but had the Wraith

353
00:20:25,876 --> 00:20:28,003
加入日内瓦协定,
attended the Geneva Convention,

354
00:20:28,128 --> 00:20:30,631
他们可能会把这的每一个人都给吃了
they would have tried to feed on everyone there.

355
00:20:32,216 --> 00:20:35,010
Beckett的报告显示，我们还无法确定
Beckett's report indicates that we have no idea

356
00:20:35,094 --> 00:20:37,554
这种药对于人的长期效用
what the long-term effect
of this drug on humans might be.

357
00:20:37,596 --> 00:20:38,931
但是，我们很清楚
Well, we know damn well what

358
00:20:38,972 --> 00:20:41,183
要是幽灵入侵了，我们会怎样，不是么?
the long-term effects of Wraith culling are, don't we?

359
00:20:41,308 --> 00:20:42,726
我们在说的是把一个活人
We're talking about putting a human being

360
00:20:42,726 --> 00:20:45,437
和一个饿得要死的幽灵放在一个房间里
in the same room as a starving Wraith.

361
00:20:46,063 --> 00:20:47,689
一旦我们开始前进
Now once we start down that road...

362
00:20:47,815 --> 00:20:50,150
你觉得我们该怎么走哪条?
Which road did you think we were headed down?

363
00:20:50,192 --> 00:20:51,110
不是这条
Not this one.

364
00:20:52,194 --> 00:20:54,279
至少不是这么快
At least not this fast.

365
00:20:55,155 --> 00:20:59,284
花时间在犯人身上，我不同情他
Having spent time with the prisoner, I don't pity him.

366
00:20:59,451 --> 00:21:01,578
无论如何，他都是要死的
He's gonna die anyway.

367
00:21:04,498 --> 00:21:06,792
这种药将来或许会很有用
This drug could be useful some day.

368
00:21:06,917 --> 00:21:08,293
将来
Some day.

369
00:21:08,585 --> 00:21:12,172
关键是，这样的机会不多
The point is, we don't get
a lot of opportunities like this.

370
00:21:12,423 --> 00:21:14,508
你知道
Do you know how obsessed with this the Hoffans are

371
00:21:14,508 --> 00:21:17,428
当HOFFENS知道我们抓了一个幽灵时有多迷惑?
when they found out we had a live Wraith prisoner?

372
00:21:18,470 --> 00:21:20,973
他反正时要死的
He's going to die.

373
00:21:21,473 --> 00:21:22,975
我们试着给他吃各种各样活的东西
I've tried to feed him all sorts of life stuff

374
00:21:22,975 --> 00:21:25,602
但是看起来他只吃一样
but apparently there's only one item on his menu.

375
00:21:26,437 --> 00:21:27,354
测试人是谁?
What about the test subject?

376
00:21:28,105 --> 00:21:29,440
如果失败了
If the drug fails...

377
00:21:29,565 --> 00:21:31,692
我们不是从大街上随便抓一个人来
We're not just grabbing anybody off the street.

378
00:21:31,859 --> 00:21:34,319
这个人得了绝症，晚期了
The test subject is a terminally ill

379
00:21:34,361 --> 00:21:36,405
他自愿的
patient who has volunteered himself.

380
00:21:38,115 --> 00:21:40,325
这不是一个决定
These are not exactly the type of decisions

381
00:21:40,325 --> 00:21:43,287
我想试试
I was expecting to make on this expedition.

382
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:56,508
做吧
Do it.

383
00:22:09,730 --> 00:22:10,898
嗨, Steve
Hi, Steve.

384
00:22:11,815 --> 00:22:13,734
还要样本?
More samples?

385
00:22:13,817 --> 00:22:16,612
我想沿着一片田地
I was thinking more along the lines of a field trip.

386
00:22:16,904 --> 00:22:17,988
你想要食物么?
You want sustenance?

387
00:22:18,739 --> 00:22:20,574
我要信息
I want information.

388
00:22:23,077 --> 00:22:26,663
你无法提供这样的交易
You are incapable of offering such a trade.

389
00:22:27,414 --> 00:22:32,044
如果你告诉我一些有价值的东西，我给你吃的
You tell me something of value, I let you eat.

390
00:22:32,252 --> 00:22:33,212
这就是你的晚餐
That's the deal.

391
00:22:33,337 --> 00:22:35,756
要或不要
Take it or leave it.

392
00:22:39,843 --> 00:22:41,386
很好
Very well.

393
00:22:51,146 --> 00:22:52,606
他们准备好了么?
Are they ready?

394
00:22:53,023 --> 00:22:56,693
Sheppard少校和Ford少尉
正将犯人送去探险者2号
Major Sheppard and Lieutenant Ford
are loading the prisoner into Jumper Two.

395
00:22:56,693 --> 00:22:58,695
bates军士也准备好了
Sergeant bates is already on the ground

396
00:22:58,737 --> 00:23:02,783
在集合地点等待他们的降落
and standing by for their arrival
at the rendezvous site.

397
00:23:20,884 --> 00:23:22,052
探险者2号, 我是Weir
Jumper Two, this is Weir.

398
00:23:22,136 --> 00:23:23,178
你现在怎样?
What's your status?

399
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:23,971
很好
Nice and cosy in here.

400
00:23:24,012 --> 00:23:25,848
准备出发
We're ready to depart.

401
00:23:25,889 --> 00:23:27,099
注意安全 少校
Be safe, Major.

402
00:23:27,474 --> 00:23:28,809
这就是计划
That's the plan.

403
00:23:29,101 --> 00:23:31,019
探险者2号，准备发射
Jumper Two, you are go for launch.

404
00:23:31,061 --> 00:23:32,229
Roger
Roger that.

405
00:23:33,564 --> 00:23:34,982
拉起来
Dial it up.

406
00:23:41,196 --> 00:23:43,490
嗨，伙计，这并不有趣
Hey, man, this isn't supposed to be fun.

407
00:24:04,094 --> 00:24:06,638
Perna 跟我说了你的病情
Perna explained to me about your illness.

408
00:24:07,431 --> 00:24:09,767
我希望你知道我很抱歉
I want you to know how sorry I am.

409
00:24:10,642 --> 00:24:12,895
我希望可以帮你做点什么
I wish there was something I could do for you.

410
00:24:13,562 --> 00:24:14,855
时间到了, Beckett博士
It's my time, Doctor Beckett.

411
00:24:15,814 --> 00:24:17,983
现在看我的运气吧
I'm at peace with my fate.

412
00:24:19,068 --> 00:24:20,986
我希望你知道，这很重要，
I think it's important you know

413
00:24:21,153 --> 00:24:24,740
或许结果没有想得那么好
that we may be talking about a
less than peaceful ending here.

414
00:24:24,865 --> 00:24:28,619
我已经跟 Merell 详细的解释过会发生什么事情
I have explained to Merell in
great detail what may befall him.

415
00:24:30,454 --> 00:24:33,540
你必须明白这种药物重来没有使用过
You should also understand
that this drug has never worked

416
00:24:33,624 --> 00:24:36,251
除了在实验室不断的模拟试验
in anything other than a laboratory simulation.

417
00:24:36,835 --> 00:24:39,004
我们无法确定会发生什么事情
We don't know for certain what will happen.

418
00:24:40,089 --> 00:24:41,548
就算没有用,
Even if it doesn't work,

419
00:24:42,508 --> 00:24:43,759
你也可以知道一些有价值的信息
you'll learn something of value

420
00:24:45,928 --> 00:24:47,971
将来如何完善它?
how to perfect it in the future?

421
00:24:48,847 --> 00:24:53,477
或许，但你没有理由去面对那些生物
Possibly, but that's no reason
for you to face that creature.

422
00:24:55,104 --> 00:24:57,439
Beckett博士, 我不害怕
Doctor Beckett, I'm not afraid.

423
00:24:58,607 --> 00:25:01,485
不管发生什么事情，我的死都会很有意义
No matter what happens, my death will have meaning.

424
00:25:03,278 --> 00:25:05,114
这不就是我们努力争取的么,
Is that not something we all strive for,

425
00:25:05,239 --> 00:25:07,241
死得有意义?
to die knowing we made a difference?

426
00:25:09,034 --> 00:25:10,702
我想这么做
I want to do this.

427
00:25:11,745 --> 00:25:14,665
请不要让我失去这个为人民服务的机会
Please don't deny me the chance to help my people.

428
00:25:24,466 --> 00:25:25,717
你怎么看?
What do you think?

429
00:25:25,968 --> 00:25:27,886
我实在无法相信
That it goes against everything I believe in.

430
00:25:28,053 --> 00:25:31,223
在我的家乡，学医的人之中流传一种诅咒
There's an oath among medical people where I come from.

431
00:25:31,348 --> 00:25:33,308
刚开始，并没有什么害处
It begins, First, do no harm.

432
00:25:33,976 --> 00:25:37,271
- 对你很重要的话
- 不止这些Perna
- Important words to you.
- More than words, Perna.

433
00:25:38,439 --> 00:25:41,650
试验就要开始了
The battle rages at the very
threshold of our laboratory now.

434
00:25:42,151 --> 00:25:44,153
我们努力工作到最好，知道
Those of us working to the last know

435
00:25:44,194 --> 00:25:46,697
这最后的一点时间是很宝贵的,
that these few final hours have been dearly purchased,

436
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:49,575
我们的注意力还没有消减
yet our concentration has not waned.

437
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:52,119
我们无法期望自救
We cannot hope to save ourselves

438
00:25:52,161 --> 00:25:54,997
但是我们可以希望最后一点有力的发现,
but we can hope that one last insight,

439
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:58,208
在我们还剩最后一口气之前,
one last revelation before we take our dying breaths,

440
00:25:58,333 --> 00:26:02,337
可能可以阻止这样恐怖的事情再次发生
may prevent this terrible day from happening again.

441
00:26:02,629 --> 00:26:04,798
Ferrel的最后一次日记
Ferrel's last journal entry.

442
00:26:05,424 --> 00:26:07,509
什么都别说, Carson
More than words, Carson.

443
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:08,594
我明白
I understand that.

444
00:26:08,969 --> 00:26:09,511
我了解
I do.

445
00:26:09,678 --> 00:26:11,138
但是还有很多人不知道
But there are too many unknowns.

446
00:26:11,221 --> 00:26:12,681
我们需要时间来确定它的副作用
We need time to determine the possible side-effects...

447
00:26:12,765 --> 00:26:13,849
没有时间了!
There is no time!

448
00:26:14,641 --> 00:26:16,685
你这么害怕犯错么
Are you so afraid of making a mistake

449
00:26:16,769 --> 00:26:19,354
那你永远也无法知道我们要面临的是什么?
that you can no longer see what we're up against?

450
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:22,107
不是害怕犯错 Perna,
This isn't about making mistakes Perna,

451
00:26:22,149 --> 00:26:24,610
这是方法问题,
it's about the end justifying the means,

452
00:26:24,860 --> 00:26:27,696
对于我们的专业而言，这是个灾难
and in our profession that's a very slippery slope.

453
00:26:29,448 --> 00:26:31,533
我们并不确定这一定有效
We have no idea if this'll work.

454
00:26:32,034 --> 00:26:34,953
我们可能是将这个人送给了一个怪物
We could be sacrificing that man to a monster.

455
00:26:35,579 --> 00:26:37,873
还会有其他人接替他的位置
There will be another to take his place.

456
00:26:39,750 --> 00:26:41,627
这就是我害怕的
That's just what I'm afraid of.

457
00:26:48,592 --> 00:26:49,843
他们好了
They are ready.

458
00:26:54,473 --> 00:26:55,933
当心
Careful, sir.

459
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:10,697
这就是你承诺的食物?
This is the sustenance you promised?

460
00:27:10,739 --> 00:27:13,325
计划有点变动
Little change in plans.

461
00:27:13,992 --> 00:27:18,747
你现在就告诉我，否则就什么都没有了
You tell me something right now,
or the damned party's cancelled.

462
00:27:18,956 --> 00:27:20,416
你想知道什么?
What do you want to know?

463
00:27:20,749 --> 00:27:22,793
还有多少舰队
How many hive ships have become operational

464
00:27:22,835 --> 00:27:24,878
自从我们唤醒了第一个?
since we awakened the first one?

465
00:27:25,045 --> 00:27:27,172
所有, Sheppard少校
All of them, Major Sheppard.

466
00:27:27,464 --> 00:27:32,469
首先，他们会去饲养基地，增强力量
First, they will travel to their own
feeding grounds and gather strength.

467
00:27:33,095 --> 00:27:35,347
我们是很有忍耐力的民族, 少校
We are a patient race, Major.

468
00:27:36,181 --> 00:27:39,685
当我们的力量完全聚集之后,
When we have taken our fill and gathered our strength,

469
00:27:40,018 --> 00:27:43,689
就会向你们发起攻击
we will join force and come for you.

470
00:27:43,772 --> 00:27:45,566
什么时候?
D'you have any idea when that'll be?

471
00:27:45,816 --> 00:27:46,400
早上?
Morning?

472
00:27:46,442 --> 00:27:48,026
下午?
Afternoon?

473
00:27:51,655 --> 00:27:52,781
打开
Open it up.

474
00:28:05,169 --> 00:28:06,920
你不需要这么做
You don't have to do this.

475
00:28:08,338 --> 00:28:08,839
我知道
I know.

476
00:28:11,717 --> 00:28:13,010
我准备好了
I'm ready.

477
00:28:40,704 --> 00:28:42,456
他很虚弱
He is weak.

478
00:29:29,906 --> 00:29:32,408
你们都是Hoffan人民的英雄
You are both heroes of the Hoffan people.

479
00:29:32,909 --> 00:29:34,744
我承认，这很疯狂
I'll admit, it was amazing.

480
00:29:35,328 --> 00:29:36,954
我希望你的朋友也能加入我们
I hope your friends will join us for

481
00:29:36,996 --> 00:29:38,831
的一个为你办的庆功宴
a celebratory banquet to honour your work.

482
00:29:39,207 --> 00:29:40,374
我们很愿意参加，但是你
We'll be glad to attend, but don't you

483
00:29:40,416 --> 00:29:42,585
觉不觉得庆功宴有点太早了?
think celebrations are a bit premature?

484
00:29:42,794 --> 00:29:44,879
这个结果
The results speak for themselves.

485
00:29:45,129 --> 00:29:47,048
我打算让议会通过
I intend to ask the Council to approve

486
00:29:47,089 --> 00:29:49,342
大批量生产这种血清,立即生效
mass production of the serum, effective immediately.

487
00:29:49,425 --> 00:29:52,470
今天之后,
我想不会有任何异议
After what happened today,
I doubt they will offer any resistance.

488
00:29:52,553 --> 00:29:54,347
这真是个好消息，长官
That is wonderful news, Chancellor.

489
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:56,057
值得尊重，不
With all due respect, no it isn't.

490
00:29:56,474 --> 00:29:58,434
我们现在在说的是一个测试
We're talking about one test here.

491
00:29:58,935 --> 00:30:01,354
对于这个结果我和大家一样高兴
Now I'm as pleased as anyone with the results

492
00:30:01,562 --> 00:30:02,939
但是我们还要很多事情要做
but we still have a lot of work to do

493
00:30:02,980 --> 00:30:04,607
在我们开始将它投入生产之前
before we can start using it.

494
00:30:04,816 --> 00:30:08,277
Beckett 博士希望可以进行一系列测试
Doctor Beckett wishes to run a full series of tests

495
00:30:08,402 --> 00:30:11,280
对这个结果进行反覆论证
on Merell prior to issuing his final report.

496
00:30:11,405 --> 00:30:12,615
可能会有些副作用
There may have been mitigating circumstances

497
00:30:12,657 --> 00:30:14,575
比如说，这个人可能会死
the man was dying, for one.

498
00:30:16,369 --> 00:30:16,911
当然
Of course.

499
00:30:17,328 --> 00:30:18,663
我会跟议会说明的
I'll bring it up with Council.

500
00:30:19,664 --> 00:30:21,374
为了成功
To success.

501
00:30:25,211 --> 00:30:26,003
怎么了?
What is it?

502
00:30:26,129 --> 00:30:28,089
Steve看起来好像很难受
It's Steve he doesn't look so good.

503
00:30:31,050 --> 00:30:32,677
他这个样子多久了?
How long has he been like this?

504
00:30:33,136 --> 00:30:34,220
测试之后
Since the test.

505
00:30:34,262 --> 00:30:35,513
是不是什么诡计?
Think it's a ruse?

506
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,223
他们不会来这套
It is not their way.

507
00:30:43,271 --> 00:30:43,896
嗨
Hey.

508
00:30:46,107 --> 00:30:47,692
你对我做了什么?
What have you done to me?

509
00:31:04,959 --> 00:31:06,377
叫Beckett过来
We need Beckett in here.

510
00:31:06,419 --> 00:31:07,462
快去
Go.

511
00:31:14,594 --> 00:31:16,053
我们会帮你的
We're gonna help you.

512
00:31:18,931 --> 00:31:20,850
不需要你的可怜
Don't feel pity for me.

513
00:31:22,477 --> 00:31:26,022
其他幽灵来的时候，你们会比我现在更惨
You will suffer far worse when the others come for you.

514
00:31:49,587 --> 00:31:50,213
少校
Major.

515
00:31:51,047 --> 00:31:52,924
我正准备把他解剖
I was just about to cut him open.

516
00:31:53,382 --> 00:31:55,468
那我先走
Then, I was just leaving.

517
00:31:55,802 --> 00:31:59,305
我已经做了一系列的测试，你可能对结果会有兴趣
I've already done a series of tests
you might like to know the results of.

518
00:31:59,806 --> 00:32:01,099
你知道是什么使他死去的么?
You know what killed him?

519
00:32:01,224 --> 00:32:02,892
我检查了他身体的一部分，发现，
I'm gonna go out on a limb here and say

520
00:32:03,017 --> 00:32:06,562
他体内的重要器官几乎同时停止工作
that it was all of his vital organs
shutting down almost simultaneously.

521
00:32:06,813 --> 00:32:08,147
他是饿死的么?
Did he starve to death?

522
00:32:08,272 --> 00:32:08,898
不
No.

523
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,817
取决于他的体制,
Based on the condition his body's in,

524
00:32:10,942 --> 00:32:12,902
我觉得他不是饿死的
I don't think he died from a lack of nourishment.

525
00:32:12,944 --> 00:32:14,112
那么是什么?
