Does the vote include all your people?

701
00:42:02,926 --> 00:42:04,302
每个人
Every one.

702
00:42:04,302 --> 00:42:08,848
你看到了, 少校,我们都很一致，大家都很坚决
So you see, Major, we speak with one voice,
and we are resolute.

703
00:42:08,890 --> 00:42:09,557
是的
Yeah.

704
00:42:09,724 --> 00:42:10,767
我明白了
I can see that.

705
00:42:11,851 --> 00:42:14,062
下次我们见面的时候，我希望可以讨论比较好的办法
When next we meet, I would like to discuss the best way

706
00:42:14,187 --> 00:42:16,773
尽可能的把药分到世界的各个角落
to disseminate the drug on as many worlds as possible.

707
00:42:16,981 --> 00:42:19,275
我们不会很快久这么做的
We won't be doing that any time soon.

708
00:42:19,484 --> 00:42:21,820
或许我们的胜利会让你改变主意
Perhaps our victory will change your mind.

709
00:42:21,861 --> 00:42:26,032
但我们回来的时候，我不认为你还会在
If and when we ever return,
I don't imagine you'll be here.

710
00:42:27,033 --> 00:42:29,953
我也不认为还会有任何人的存在
I don't imagine anybody else will be, either.

711
00:42:40,213 --> 00:42:41,673
好运
Good luck.

712
00:42:47,887 --> 00:42:49,431
"不计任何代价的胜利"
"Victory at all costs".

713
00:42:49,472 --> 00:42:51,433
听起来很耳熟, 少校?
That sound familiar, Major?

714
00:42:52,100 --> 00:42:52,976
Churchill
Churchill.

715
00:42:53,101 --> 00:42:53,518
是
Aye.

716
00:42:53,560 --> 00:42:56,354
我决不会同意的


Never thought I'd disagree.

